		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#00aeef"><strong>A BIG THANK YOU FROM THE  STAFFING TEAM</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>It's been one hell of a summer, but we did it! All ten of our summer 'waves' are now finished, and the teams have taken their social action projects to their local communities to raise awareness for their chosen topic. All that's left for us to do now is say a massive thank you to everyone who supported the NCS programme over the last few months!</p>

<p>This summer we worked with an incredible 27,070 young people, all of whom bonded with their teams to make a change in their local communities. None of this would have been possible without your help.</p>

<p>We'd still love to hear all about your experiences this summer - rememeber to share your memorable stories with <strong>@seasonalstaff</strong> on Twitter, or on our <strong>Seasonal Staff</strong> Facebook page!</p></td>

					
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
