<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#ea007a"><strong>NCS AUTUMN 2015 - WHO'S READY?</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>We're just weeks away from the beginning of the NCS Autumn programme; a shortened programme which takes place in the October half term. We can't wait for the Autumn waves to start - we hope you're excited too!</p>

<p>If you're set to work with us during October and/or November, now's the time to make sure that we have all of your correct personal information. Please head to the <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/Login.aspx?ReturnUrl=%2fsecure%2f" target="_blank">Staffing Website</a> to ensure that your health & safety information, emergency contact details, and bank & tax information is all up to date.</p>

<p>If you've signed up for the Autumn programme but haven't had any job placements confirmed yet, please do get in touch with your <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/contact/" target="_blank">local Staffing team</a> to make sure that they know your full availability. Please note: as the Autumn programme is much shorter than our Summer one, we will prioritise candidates who are available for the entirety of their chosen Autumn wave.</p>

<p>See you in October!</p></td>
			
						
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-rightsideimg-comm1_211014.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="200" border="0"><br>
			<img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-rightsideimg-group1_211014.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="200" border="0"><br>
			<img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-actv1_211014.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="270" border="0"></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
