		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p><strong>Think Ahead</strong><br>
			<a href="http://thinkahead.org/" target="_blank">Think Ahead </a> is a new fast-track programme for graduates and career-changers remarkable enough to make a real difference to people with mental health problems.</p>

<p>We're searching for exceptional people to become mental health social workers. You will study for a Post-Graduate Diploma and a Master's qualification in Social Work from the University of York. You'll be paid to work in an expert team alongside clinical professionals, study for a master's degree and develop your leadership skills.</p>

<p>We're here to find remarkable people, who'll do remarkable things. Think Ahead: apply your mind to mental health.</p>

<p>Applications are now <a href="http://thinkahead.org/" target="_blank">open</a> to take part in our two-year programme from July 2016.<br>
			<br>
			
			
			</td><td align="right" valign="top"><img src="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/Think_Ahead_logo.JPG" alt="" width="200" height="" border="0"></td>
			
